<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="rosetta"
>
<body>

<metal:portlets fill-slot="portlets">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-countrylangs" />
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-browserlangs" />
</metal:portlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main" >

  <h1 tal:condition="not: view/is_current_user">
    <span tal:replace="context/fmt:displayname">Someone</span>'s
    language preferences
  </h1>

  <h1 tal:condition="view/is_current_user">
    Your language preferences
  </h1>

  <p class="documentDescription">
    Your preferred languages are used to configure some Launchpad applications
    to work with the languages you know. Launchpad Translations allows you
    to translate a project into your preferred languages. Launchpad Answers
    allows you to ask and answer questions in your preferred languages.
    Launchpad's default language is English, which is the only language for
    most Launchpad features.
  </p>

  <form action="" method="post">
    <input name="redirection_url" type="hidden"
           tal:attributes="value view/getRedirectionURL" />
    <div class="listbox">
      <div tal:repeat="language view/visible_checked_languages">
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" checked="checked"
                 tal:attributes="name language/code;" />
          <span tal:replace="language/englishname">Spanish</span>
        </label>
        <hr tal:condition="repeat/language/end" style="margin:0px; height:2px;" />
      </div>
      <div tal:repeat="language view/visible_unchecked_languages">
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox"
                 tal:attributes="name language/code;" />
          <span tal:replace="language/englishname">Spanish</span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="actions" style="text-align: right;">
      <input type="submit" name="SAVE-LANGS" value="Save" />
    </div>
  </form>

</div>

<div metal:fill-slot="help">
  <p>
    Please select the languages that you speak well.  There are many languages
    to choose from.  Once you have selected your preferred languages,
    Launchpad knows which ones you are most interested in and can avoid
    bothering you with the full list.
  </p>
  <ul class="info">
    <li>
      <a href="https://help.launchpad.net/RosettaFAQ"
        >Frequently asked questions</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</body>
</html>
